GoldenEye::

She took the CR supplies to the transport pod. She saw Bludgeon and 
Obsidian there. "Hello there. How are you guys doing?" She smiled at 
Bludgeon. "I got two more crates to load,would you help me with 
that?" She smiled at both bots now.
